[SHORT DESC]
Increases chances of successfully escaping a random battle.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>If the wielder is in battle, it will be guaranteed the ability to flee so long as it isn't under the effects of full-trapping moves or abilities. This does not apply to trainer battles, where fleeing cannot occur. This does not allow escape from the trapping abilities <a href="/bw/abilities/shadow_tag">Shadow Tag</a> or <a href="/bw/abilities/arena_trap">Arena Trap</a>, the moves <a href="/bw/moves/mean_look">Mean Look</a> and <a href="/bw/moves/spide_web">Spider Web</a>, or the trapping effects of moves such as <a href="/bw/moves/fire_spin">Fire Spin</a> and <a href="/bw/moves/whirlpool">Whirlpool</a>.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Has no use in link or Wi-Fi battles.</p>